The paper discusses the need for dedicated ranking functions for different domains and the blending of documents from different sources into a single ranking list. This suggests that the paper is related to information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
